    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1" facs="#D_000146-037-000-facs001-l001-p001"/>
            <p xml:id="uuid_4fc1aec9-60dc-4ab6-8a8b-309d81f13146" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_2cb7a046-594a-4e76-b7a0-46594aee761d"/>L/S 16. April [193]1 </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_aac5b0a5-ba69-4bc5-84b2-ac247fd749e2" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_18ecfabf-d4e8-46cd-acfa-bfd4e886cd70"/><hi rend="spaced">Antrag</hi>
                <lb xml:id="uuid_75a703e0-ed1b-4e4e-a703-e0ed1bee4ece"/>auf Ladung zum
                Offenbarungseid. </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_f9eb3f79-df71-4db8-9460-64c5a1dabc3e" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_98ae01fa-ae71-4dbf-ae01-faae719dbf9d"/>In Sachen <lb xml:id="uuid_c362ffec-6c00-47de-a2ff-ec6c00a7deb6"/>des Schriftstellers <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11988">Karl <hi rend="spaced">Kraus</hi></rs>, <lb xml:id="uuid_e9a25c5a-f6b1-49ea-a25c-5af6b1b9eae0"/><rs type="place" subtype="address" ref="#pmb50496">Wien III, Hintere Zollamtsstr. 3</rs>, <lb xml:id="uuid_01300451-079b-4639-b004-51079b1639e8"/>Klägers, </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_bb95589e-ef39-469d-8808-329be7d61ad6" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_9bdc2f60-a350-434d-9c2f-60a350b34d80"/>Prozessbevollmächtigte: <lb xml:id="uuid_2394a207-f3fd-4acc-94a2-07f3fd9accb5"/>Rechtsanwälte Dr. <rs type="person" ref="#pmb38969">Botho
                    Laserstein</rs> , <lb xml:id="uuid_d288cab7-3bea-420b-88ca-b73bea420b06"/>Dr.
                    <rs type="person" ref="#pmb52922">Gerhard Badrian</rs>, <lb xml:id="uuid_192b99ba-df34-459d-ab99-badf34759db6"/><rs type="place" subtype="address" ref="#pmb51751">Berlin NO.18, Landsberger Allee 115/116</rs>, </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_f71ab62b-a045-446c-a6dc-b2ae5748dedc" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_6a9ef00d-5e55-45e3-9ef0-0d5e55c5e328"/><hi rend="spaced">gegen</hi>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_5e8b72f4-c056-4517-9d1b-8306315998dd" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_6e205371-0933-4863-a053-710933c86309"/>den Theaterdirektor <rs type="person" ref="#pmb37761">Ernst Josef <hi rend="spaced">Aufricht</hi></rs>, <lb xml:id="uuid_4d27a1fd-7f16-4efc-a7a1-fd7f16defc97"/><rs type="place" subtype="address" ref="#pmb56965">Berlin W., Landauer Strasse 4</rs>, <lb xml:id="uuid_ace0d297-9798-4bc6-a0d2-9797983bc63e"/>Beklagten, </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_eb2ad309-a696-4c47-93ec-7d0d8b935e1d" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_b99327e8-54a7-4c49-9327-e854a72c497c"/>hat die Zwangsvollstreckung
                aus <lb xml:id="uuid_8e47a4a9-9462-4820-87a4-a99462582012"/>dem anliegenden <rs type="work">Vollstreckungstitel</rs>
                <lb xml:id="uuid_24f652e5-ad70-458c-b652-e5ad70958cc3"/>laut dem anliegenden <rs type="work">Pfändungspro<lb xml:id="uuid_08dbd17a-d7bf-4538-9bd1-7ad7bf5538c4" break="no"/>tokoll</rs> zu einer Befriedigung des <lb xml:id="uuid_fcf67ff0-77d8-4725-b67f-f077d8672527"/><rs type="person" ref="#pmb11988">Gläubigers</rs> nicht geführt. </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_cbf9892e-ab5b-45c2-9d3a-b0e6894e72ca" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_f154bede-e32b-454d-94be-dee32b554d9b"/>Ich beantrage daher namens
                    <lb xml:id="uuid_9b999175-4028-4f43-9991-7540282f43e9"/>des <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11988">Gläubigers</rs>: </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_d2dbf2f5-a3a1-4cbb-a588-b9dd76943aff" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_c0d02bb3-6074-413f-902b-b36074213f23"/>Die Bestimmung eines Termins
                    <lb xml:id="uuid_132aa78a-af17-4a65-aaa7-8aaf174a6584"/>zur Leistung des
                    Offenbarungs<lb xml:id="uuid_084ebe70-7a17-4588-8ebe-707a17458848" break="no"/>eides wegen: </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_5a06bda9-fb88-4574-bc20-9ea2ddb7055f" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_ae528eb8-c2cf-4ba2-928e-b8c2cf3ba21b"/>1. Festgesetzte Kosten R:
                213.75 <lb xml:id="uuid_2aa3b089-5011-4d4f-a3b0-895011fd4fc9"/>2. Gebühr für diesen
                Antrag 4.50 <lb xml:id="uuid_8742d732-784f-43fc-82d7-32784f33fcac"/>3.
                Vollstreckungsgebühr 5.35 <lb xml:id="uuid_084a1e96-e7b2-47e2-8a1e-96e7b267e2f1"/>4.
                Porti hierfür 0.45 <lb xml:id="uuid_660b29ec-a5e3-4d41-8b29-eca5e35d416e"/>5.
                Umsatzsteuer 0.10 <lb xml:id="uuid_860464bf-ff33-4fbd-8464-bfff337fbdc8"/>224.15 </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_bd8a638a-6d68-4c96-94ad-2df3035913f0" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_82f19fec-7c4e-4eb5-b19f-ec7c4edeb571"/>An das <lb xml:id="uuid_ab8a0bae-7fc3-464e-8a0b-ae7fc3764e58"/><rs type="institution" ref="#pmb36362">Amtsgericht <lb xml:id="uuid_164691bd-ff8f-4c9c-8691-bdff8fec9c01"/>Berlin-Charlottenburg</rs>. <pb n="2" facs="#D_000146-037-000-facs001-l001-p002"/>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_50624e63-5f6c-4b47-8f09-c9b81961d9dd" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_7b9cc403-948a-4ab7-9cc4-03948aeab7e3"/>Im Falle der Eidesleistung
                bitte ich, mir <lb xml:id="uuid_69625855-4ee3-4162-a258-554ee3e16272"/>eine
                Abschrift des Vermögensverzeichnisses zu über<lb xml:id="uuid_e06df0ce-6092-4f06-adf0-ce60929f06af" break="no"/>senden. </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_b017dd14-cc9e-46e5-8d44-603339d577fc" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_60797a23-fae1-4877-b97a-23fae1787754"/>Im Falle der Nichtleistung
                des Eides beantrage <lb xml:id="uuid_e137c809-4387-46ac-b7c8-09438786ac34"/>ich: </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_9976835b-4b8c-46b4-9d87-34455f523633" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_cae3638a-706c-4ff1-a363-8a706c8ff115"/>Erlass und Zusendung des
                Haftbefehls. </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_939d1a41-bcd3-4576-81b1-0a537806af1b" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_ca0fd031-1e67-4710-8fd0-311e676710e5"/><rs type="person" ref="#pmb38969">Rechtsanwalt</rs>.</p>
        </body>
